      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The chassis remains uncompromisingly rigid, having undergone professional subframe reinforcement. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential, providing the visceral analog feedback and balanced lateral dynamics synonymous with the M-division. The factory finish exhibits exceptional depth, and the cabin remains in a time-capsule state with no bolster wear or pixel degradation. A meticulously maintained example for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
